title: New Wasm Project Brings Web Components to Backend Languages
author: Loraine Lawson
description: An open source WebAssembly project brings web components to other languages, allowing devs to share web components across digital properties.
cntitle: WebAssembly 新项目将 Web 组件引入后端语言
cndescription: 一个开源 WebAssembly 项目将 Web 组件引入其他语言，允许开发者在数字资产间共享 Web 组件。
